NAME
       Algorithm::HITS - Perl implementation of HITS algorithm

DESCRIPTION
       This module implements the HITS algorithm (Kleinberg's
       hypertext-induced topic selection).

       See also <http://www2002.org/CDROM/refer-
       eed/643/node1.html>

